title: Battlefield 2: Project Reality v1.2.0.0
description:
------- ------ ----- ---- --- -- - -- --- ---- ----- ------ -------
YOU NEED A COPY OF BATTLEFIELD 2 TO PLAY
------- ------ ----- ---- --- -- - -- --- ---- ----- ------ -------

Project Reality: Battlefield 2 is a free-to-download single and multiplayer game modification for the Battlefield 2 PC game. Project Reality installs alongside your existing Battlefield 2 game installation, allowing both the original game and Project Reality to be played separately without conflict.

------- ------ ----- ---- --- -- - -- --- ---- ----- ------ -------
Installation Instructions
------- ------ ----- ---- --- -- - -- --- ---- ----- ------ -------

Install Battlefield 2

Install v1.41 and v1.50 patch

Install Project Reality

Enjoy!
